After hes killed by the righteous leader of his own guild, Woojin gets a chance to start over. This time hes not interested in saving the world from monstershes got his sights set on revenge! His high-level kills quickly garner him notoriety among the game plebs, while boosting his stats as he masterminds his way closer to the top. But there's something no one can figure out: whose side hes playing for. Now that he knows how to play to win, Woojin will stop at nothing to destroy the hero!
(Source: Tapas)

Jobless and down on his luck, stock trader Jang Taesan was wandering aimlessly when he saw a speeding car racing toward a child. Though he saves the childs life, he dies in the process. Reborn 14 years in the past, Taesan is a high schooler again, but he still remembers everything, including every top stock! With his familys finances in tatters, its up to him to use his market foresight to change their fate. He may have failed in his past life, but this time his success will be legendary!
(Source: Tapas)
